{"tid":947161,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登有愛］我部手機由香港默默地飛咗去日本....","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T05:56:02.000Z","uid":58547,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"47538c871f76de23e6fb8f9a5ed31b558923ce4a","tid":947161,"uid":58547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC開<br />\n<br />\n我今日搭UO 33由羽田番香港<br />\n拎行李先發現唔見咗手機 <br />\n已經即時同地勤講<br />\n佢話搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我一直都有開Find my iPhone嘅<br />\n喺香港Find my iPhone 冇反應因爲張卡係日本卡<br />\n直至岩岩我喺手機見到我手機喺37分鐘之前去左福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTimeline係<br />\n5點落機, 地勤話6點做清潔<br />\n咁岩有班UO 600由香港飛往福岡7:40起, 11:52到<br />\n即係香港時間10:52到<br />\n而我部手機喺12:00香港時間顯示喺福岡<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知係我自己唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係入面真係有好多好多好重要嘅相 希望有人可以幫到我"},{"pid":"ecd03009d5f69ee3a12456942200e07514f50b13","tid":947161,"uid":58547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrPGZZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrPGZZR.png&h=614bc6a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cebc8c09c7c8fe451948c7653fe38272fd3cf5ba","tid":947161,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b866c44c18e58bfa6782dbf518e586b95ebf4b4","tid":947161,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:14: